perturbation.changed_text:
FCC warrants to Flotek that:

(a) all of the Terpene Product supplied by FCC to Flotek shall:

(i) conform to the specifications set forth in Section 1;

(ii) comply with all relevant laws and regulations including, without limitation, laws and regulations of each of the jurisdictions in which the Terpene Product are either manufactured or to be sold or used concerning purity, sanitation, safety, security, and packaging and labeling of food and beverage, to the best of FCC's knowledge;

(iii) be in good condition at the time of delivery in all respects; and

(iv) be free from any defect in design, workmanship, materials and packaging, provided that FCC's liability for any such defects is limited to replacement of the defective product.
